{"tid":2428913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"理大新案11人改為1430九龍城法院提堂 現場鼓譟","createTime":"2021-03-02T02:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T06:16:24.000Z","uid":240362,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"fe661192835f053f7f50aa467636ae309d382e04","tid":2428913,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T02:03:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/localpresshk/19000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flocalpresshk%2F19000&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1xZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=6e533ea6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/localpresshk/19000</a><br />\n<br />\n#網友資訊<br />\n<br />\n//早晨<br />\n<br />\n司法機構官僚撚係狗<br />\n<br />\n九龍城有新嘅11人理大暴動案<br />\nSchedule 9:30 開始<br />\n9:33 庭入面嘅檢控主任都未收到文件 <br />\n連案件編號都唔知<br />\n<br />\n出面排咗50人 又唔派飛又無人交代點安排<br />\n法庭書記叫啲保安唔好出去 廢事俾人揼<br />\n<br />\n9:37 先叫啲被告(其他案)入庭<br />\n9:43 先話下晝2點半先上 我屌<br />\n問親個個都話唔係我跟開//"},{"pid":"0e4a1c67a198f1bdcbf2d5e9326fc45f41087814","tid":2428913,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T02:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92341be23557323010730f1f09b795d3499f294","tid":2428913,"uid":304431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T02:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><em></em>"},{"pid":"dde5c3f6c27ac3e5feac1c8ab5b32c51f1a782fd","tid":2428913,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T02:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e742f9da82d21e57da7a8192fe0775a1e3758df","tid":2428913,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T02:06:08.000Z","msg":"法庭都有卸膊操<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class